! BOTML 1

# Rely on a remote API using a named service and last reference.
# The domain is actually saved in memory and is geolocalized to its city of
# operation.
#
# Examples:
#  > Where is github.com?
#  < It is running from San Francisco.
#
#  > What is my ip?
#  < It's 93.184.216.34

@ geodomain http://freegeoip.net/json/$

> Where is *(?)
@ geodomain($).city
< It is running from $.


@ ip http://httpbin.org/ip

> ip
@ ip($).origin
< It's $.
